Text: I'm having a problem with the keygen. What the correct way of doing it? I'm just copying and pasting the info from the keygen box.

@gotbst05, select the product, you have to type any username and company name, click generate, then copy everything. including the -----BEGIN USBOVERNETWORK KEY BLOCK----- and -----END USBOVERNETWORK KEY BLOCK-----. 

Thanks chami1988, its working great.
